0I%20will%20have%20to%20sit%20our%20children%20down%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20is%20at%20the%20age%20where%20her%20friends%20will%20surely%20see%20the%20press%20and%20ask%20questions%20about%20the%20nature%20of%20these%20claims%2C%20and%20explain%20the%20cruelty%20and%20greed%20of%20people.%20I%20mourn%20yet%20another%20loss%20of%20innocence.%20Children%20should%20not%20have%20to%20endure%20such%20at%20their%20young%20age.%20It%20is%20unfair%20to%20have%20to%20try%20to%20understand%20inexplicable%20degrees%20of%20malice%20meant%20to%20destroy%20families%20and%20human%20spirit.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EMy%20heart%20and%20support%20goes%20out%20to%20true%20victims%20in%20the%20world%2C%20who%20have%20to%20watch%20how%20their%20life%20story%20is%20dressed%20in%20costume%20for%20profitability%20by%20this%20ambulance%20chaser%20in%20a%20cheap%20suit.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EYou%20have%20made%20a%20terrible%20error%20in%20judgement%20thinking%20that%20all%20%26quot%3Bcelebrities%26quot%3B%20are%20the%20same.%20I'm%20not%20from%20your%20world.%20I'm%20a%20young%20man%20who%20made%20it%20out%20of%20the%20project%20of%20Brooklyn.%20We%20don't%20play%20these%20types%20of%20games.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWe%20have%20very%20strict%20codes%20and%20honor.%20We%20protect%20children%2C%20you%20seem%20to%20exploit%20people%20for%20personal%20gain.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EOnly%20your%20network%20of%20conspiracy%20theorists%2C%20fake%20physics%2C%20will%20believe%20the%20idiotic%20claims%20you%20have%20levied%20against%20me%20that%2C%20if%20not%20for%20the%20seriousness%20surrounding%20harm%20to%20kids%2C%20would%20be%20laughable.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EI%20look%20forward%20to%20showing%20you%20just%20how%20different%20I%20am.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20Carter's%20denial%2C%20Buzbee%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20plaintiff%20never%20demanded%20money%20from%20Carter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5