%22_blank%5C%22%3Epullback%3C%2Fa%3E%20early%20next%20year%2C%20according%20to%20BCA%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrategists%20at%20firm%20said%20US%20equities%20will%20rally%20into%20January%20before%20falling%20over%2020%25%20at%20some%20point%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20year%2C%20meaning%20investors%20should%20get%20defensive%20and%20hedge%20risk.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analysts%2C%20led%20by%20chief%20US%20investment%20strategist%20Doug%20Peta%2C%20point%20to%20a%20slew%20of%20data%20points%20that%20signal%20a%20weakening%20economy%20as%20the%20tailwinds%20from%20pandemic-era%20policies%20fade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20they%20pointed%20to%20a%20slowdown%20in%20consumer%20momentum%20after%20a%20surge%20in%20%26quot%3Brevenge%20spending%26quot%3B%20following%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20data%20shows%20that%20the%20trend%20may%20be%20diminishing%2C%20even%20though%20households%20are%20broadly%20better%20off%20than%20before%20the%20pandemic.%20Compared%20to%20the%20end%20of%202019%2C%20US%20consumers%20have%20seen%20a%20surge%20in%20home%20equity%20and%20household%20wealth%20amid%20the%20stock%20market's%20stellar%20rally%2C%20the%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumer-facing%20companies%20have%20raised%20warning%20signs%20of%20less%20spending%2C%20with%20revenues%20at%20Home%20Depot%20and%20Lowe's%20slumping%20even%20amid%20surging%20home%20equity%2C%20which%20formerly%20signaled%20a%20pickup%20in%20home%20improvement%20spending.%20Earnings%20calls%20from%20other%20big%20retailers%20like%20Walmart%20and%20Target%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20have%20signaled%20a%20rise%20in%20bargain%20hunting%20as%20consumers%20tighten%20their%20budgets.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRevenge%20spending%20appears%20to%20have%20run%20its%20course%2C%20and%20a%20widening%20range%20of%20retailers%20report%20that%20consumption%20momentum%20has%20faded%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20said%20in%20a%20Monday%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20the%20BCA