%5C%22%3EChristina%20Milian%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20of%20Netflix's%20romance%20queens%2C%20and%20it's%20easy%20to%20see%20why.%20She's%20charming%20as%20Layla%2C%20our%20hero%2C%20who%20breaks%20up%20with%20her%20boyfriend%20after%20finding%20out%20he's%20cheating%20on%20her%20and%20decides%20to%20find%20the%20man%20she%20had%20a%20meet-cute%20with%20at%20an%20airport%20lounge%20the%20year%20prior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20that's%20not%20what%20the%20movie%20is%20about.%20Instead%2C%20it's%20the%20story%20of%20Layla%20actually%20falling%20in%20love%20with%20her%20personal%20concierge%2C%20Teddy%20(Devale%20Ellis).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%E2%80%A6%20why%20does%20she%20need%20a%20personal%20concierge%3F%20And%20why%20is%20the%20main%20driving%20force%20of%20this%20film%20Layla's%20desperate%20need%20to%20get%20tickets%20to%20a%20Pentatonix%20concert%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20the%20a%20cappella%20sensation%20Pentatonix%20plays%20a%20huge%20role%20in%20this%20movie%2C%20which%20unfortunately%20dates%20it%20a%20bit.%20There's%20no%20denying%20that%20the%20members%20of%20Pentatonix%20are%20talented%20(and%20they're%20pretty%20funny%20in%20the%20film)%2C%20but%20it's%20hard%20to%20believe%20anyone%20cares%20about%20them%20this%20much%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20if%20this%20movie%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpentatonix-perform-the-evolution-of-beyonc-acapella-2013-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewas%20made%20a%20decade%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20they%20were%20at%20the%20height%20of%20their%20virality%20and%20the%20a%20cappella%20craze%20led%20by%20%26quot%3BPitch%20Perfect%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BGlee%26quot%3B%20was%20still%20all%20the%20rage%2C%20but%20not%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20found%20it%20hard%20to%20tell%20tell%20if%20Layla%20lived%20in%20New%20York%20City%20or%20was%20just%20visiting%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0I%20think%20we're%20meant%20to%20believe%20she%20lives%20in%20NYC%2C%20but%20she%20acts%20like%20she's%20