%22%3A%22There%20are%202%20problems%20with%20Warren%20Buffett's%20stock%20market%20valuation%20indicator%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Warren%20Buffett%20onstage.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6706e91ba70318649280aad1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222089%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EDaniel%20Zuchnik%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Buffett%20Indicator%20is%20at%20record%20highs%2C%20signaling%20the%20stock%20market%20may%20be%20overvalued.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EYet%2C%20research%20from%20Morgan%20Stanley%20highlighted%20two%20flaws%20in%20the%20Buffett%20Indicator's%20methodology.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChanges%20in%20global%20sales%20and%20digitalization%20challenge%20traditional%20stock%20market%20valuation%20methods%20like%20the%20Buffett%20Indicator.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20stock%20market%20trading%20at%20record%20highs%2C%20Warren%20Buffett's%20favorite%20valuation%20indicator%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fwarren-buffett-valuation-signal-flashes-warning-market-cap-gdp-ratio-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eis%20also%20hitting%20new%20peaks.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Buffett%20Indicator%2C%20which%20measures%20the%20total%20market%20capitalization%20of%20US%20stocks%20relative%20to%20US%20GDP%2C%20hit%20an%20all-time%20peak%20of%20about%20209%25%20on%20Monday%2C%20surpassing%20the%20record%20high%20of%20200%25%20reached%20in%20August%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20the%20US%20stock%20market's%20total%20market%20cap%20of%20about%20%2461%20trillion%2C%20as%20measured%20by%20the%20Wilshire%205000%20index%2C%20is%20more%20than%20double%20the%20annualized%20US%20GDP%20of%20about%20%2429%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBearish%20investors%20have%20been%20quick%20to%20point%20to%20the%20Buffett%20Indicator%20as%20yet%20another%20signal%20that%20the%20stock%20market%20is%20significantly%20overvalued%20and%20due%20for%20a%20correction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20research%20from%20Morgan%20Stanley%20suggests%20the%20gauge%20may%20not%20be%20the%20best%20valuation%20tool%20to%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Mauboussin%20of%20Morgan%20Stanley's%20Counterpoint%20Globlal%20highlighted%20two%20flaws%20in%20the%20famed%20Buffett%20Indicator%2C%20which%20Buffett%20introduced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fwarren-buffett-valuation-signal-flashes-warning-market-cap-gdp-ratio-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20a%202001%20Forbes%20article.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20is%20that%20U.S.%20companies%20now%20get%20more%20of%20their%20sales%20from%20outside%20the%20U.S.%20than%20they%20did%20in%20past%20decades.%20GDP%20does%20not%20include%20those%20sales.%20That%20means%20the%20numerator%2C%20market%20capitalization%2C%20reflects%20a%20larger%20addressable%20market%20than%20what%20the%20denominator%2C%20GDP%2C%20captures%2C%26quot%3B%20Mauboussin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gauge's%20failure%20to%20capture%20foreign%20sales%20is%20a%20big%20deal%2C%20considering%20that%20about%2040%25%20of%20revenues%20derived%20from%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20companies%20come%20from%20international%20markets.%20If%20those%20revenues%20were%20encapsulated%20in%20US%20GDP%2C%20then%20the%20Buffett%20Indicator%20wouldn't%20be%20flashing%20as%20big%20of%20a%20warning%20sign%20as%20it%20is%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20flaw%20concerns%20the%20idea%20that%20the%20economy%20today%20is%20much%20different%20than%20it%20was%20in%20past%20eras.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSecond%2C%20GDP%20is%20arguably%20understated%20because%20it%20fails%20to%20measure%20accurately%20the%20quality%20of%20goods%20and%20services%20as%20well%20as%20the%20value%20of%20new%20goods%20and%20services.%20The%20rise%20of%20digitalization%20makes%20measurement%20today%20more%20challenging%20than%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20Mauboussin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhereas%20the%20GDP-based%20stock%20market%20valuation%20indicator%20may%20have%20proven%20more%20accurate%20decades%20ago%2C%20when%20manufacturing%20was%20a%20bigger%20part%20of%20America's%20economy%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-blackrock-bullish-2025-ai-mega-forces-valuations-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat's%20not%20the%20case%20today.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20from%20BlackRock%20and%20economist%20David%20Rosenberg%20recently%20has%20echoed%20this%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20equity%20market's%20changing%20sectoral%20composition%20reflects%20the%20transformation%20taking%20hold.%20So%2C%20comparing%20today's%20index%20to%20that%20of%20the%20past%20is%20like%20comparing%20apples%20to%20oranges%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-blackrock-bullish-2025-ai-mega-forces-valuations-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlackRock%20said%20last%20week.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosenberg%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20said%20last%20week%20he%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-bear-rethinking-view-ai-boom-david-rosenberg-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecalibrated%20his%20long-standing%20bearish%20view%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20the%20evolving%20nature%20of%20America's%20tech-focused%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMauboussin's%20broad%20conclusion%20from%20his%20analysis%20of%20the%20Buffett%20ratio%20is%20that%20valuation%20measures%20that%20worked%20well%20in%20the%20past%20might%20not%20be%20suited%20to%20the%20current%20market.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20with%20most%20measures%2C%20we%20need%20to%20be%20careful%20using%20it%20when%20we%20compare%20the%20present%20to%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20Mauboussin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20what%20it's%20worth%2C%20Buffett%20himself%20doesn't%20think%20his%20coined%20stock%20market%20valuation%20indicator%20is%20an%20all-encompassing%20tell%20on%20whether%20it's%20a%20good%20time%20to%20invest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20at%20Berkshire%20Hathaway's%202017%20shareholder%20meeting%20about%20his%20thoughts%20on%20valuation%20metrics%20like%20the%20Buffett%20Indicator%2C%20the%20investor%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20number%20has%20some%20degree%20of%20meaning%2C%26quot%3B%20Buffett%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20means%20more%20sometimes%20than%20others.%20%E2%80%A6%20And%20both%20of%20the%20things%20that%20you%20mentioned%20get%20bandied%20around%20a%20lot.%20It's%20not%20that%20they're%20unimportant.%20%E2%80%A6%20They%20can%20be%20very%20important.%20Sometimes%20they%20can%20be%20almost%20totally%20unimportant.%20It's%20just%20not%20quite%20as%20simple%20as%20having%20one%20or%20two%20formulas%20and%20then%20saying%20the%20market%20is%20undervalued%20or%20overvalued.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20as%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-cash-pile-berkshire-hathaway-stock-portfolio-crash-recession-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esitting%20on%20more%20than%20%24300%20billion%20in%20cash%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20investors%20and%20market%20observers%20have%20speculated%20that%20Buffett%20is%20concerned%20about%20current%20stock%20market%20valuations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-stock-market-valuation-indicator-tech-gdp-berkshire-hathaway-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733762711000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67570a18a57635a3d24d1637%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fwarren-