idth%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Cavi-art%20Black%20Seaweed%20vegan%20caviar.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F626814692bd7770018cef84f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhile%20Cavi-art's%20kelp-based%20caviar%20may%20lack%20the%20fishiness%20of%20true%20caviar%2C%20it%20more%20than%20fits%20the%20bill%20%E2%80%94%20and%20cuts%20it%20exponentially.%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGood%20approximation%20of%20caviar%20texture%2C%20great%20mixed%20into%20dishes%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDoesn't%20taste%20exactly%20like%20caviar%20(but%20nothing%20will)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20few%20takes%20on%20vegan%20caviar%20out%20there%2C%20and%20they're%20generally%20made%20from%20kelp%20or%20sea%20grape%20(%3Cem%3Ecaulerpa%20lentillifera%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20both%20of%20which%20offer%20the%20brininess%20and%20desirable%20snap%20found%20in%20the%20real%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20plenty%20happy%20with%20Cavi-art%20as%20a%20kelp-based%20alternative%2C%20especially%20when%20it's%20mixed%20into%20dishes%20that%20call%20for%20a%20dollop%20or%20two%20of%20caviar.%20I%20won't%20go%20so%20far%20as%20to%20suggest%20that%20it%20imparts%20the%20same%20richness%20of%20sturgeon%20roe%2C%20but%20combined%20with%20pasta%20or%20set%20atop%20an%20oyster%20doused%20in%20vinegar%2C%20it's%20debatable%20whether%20many%20of%20us%20could%20dissect%20the%20subtleties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrankly%2C%20and%20with%20full%20disclosure%20that%20I%20am%20an%20omnivore%2C%20I'd%20choose%20sea%20grapes%20over%20most%20legitimate%20caviar%20on%20the%20market%20today.%20Unfortunately%2C%20sea%20grapes%20are%20best%20fresh%2C%20and%20they're%20notoriously%20difficult%20to%20procure%20in%20their%20optimal%20state%20unless%20you%20have%20a%20very%20kind%20friend%20somewhere%20in%20the%20South%20Pacific.%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipg_122318_best-caviar-20%26h%3D52711702c81175874c5fee23e6ca3e3ffbf0ca280cc45a271f9bf0589b3eaf49%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f4205d%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fbest-caviar%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FOrganic-Umibudo-Sea-Grapes-Dehydrated%252Fdp%252FB08NTRLCSS%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYou%20can%20find%20them%20dehydrated%20on%20Amazon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20they're%20just%20not%20the%20same.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20Cavi-art%20gives%20you%20the%20snap%20that%20only%20four-figure%20offerings%20seem%20to%20deliver%2C%20which%20is%20a%20big%20reason%20many%20of%20us%20enjoy%20caviar%20in%20the%20first%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20Californian%20white%20sturgeon%3A%20Roe%20Caviar%20Gift%20Set%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224352%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20tin%20of%20Roe%20Caviar%20with%20a%20tiny%20spoon%20in%20it%20on%20a%20wood%20surface.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6268126b1662990018d5fedd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223264%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EOwen%20Burke%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EExtremely%20flavorful%2C%20briny%2C%20clean%20finish%2C%20some%20snap%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENot%20uniformly%20firm%20in%20texture%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaised%20in%20northern%20California%20and%20cured%20in%20salt%20for%20a%20month%2C%20this%20is%20single-origin%20roe%2C%20so%20there's%20no%20mixing%20(a%20ubiquitous%20problem%20in%20the%20caviar%20world)%2C%20and%20thus%20no%20dilution%20of%20flavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20avoiding%20the%20steeper%20price%20of%20white%20sturgeon%20roe%20compared%20to%20other%20options%20on%20our%20list%2C%20but%20if%2