%20global%20people-team%20chair%20at%20BCG%2C%20has%20been%20at%20the%20consulting%20firm%20for%20nearly%2020%20years.%20It's%20a%20testament%2C%20she%20said%2C%20to%20the%20company's%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20place%20built%20to%20make%20talent%20do%20things%20that%20they%20didn't%20even%20know%20they%20could%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Pittman%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20included%20in%20that.%20I%20love%20the%20learning%20that%20comes%20with%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPittman%20said%20one%20aspect%20of%20leadership%20development%20she's%20focused%20on%20is%20ethical%20practices.%20%26quot%3BWe%20teach%20and%20train%20our%20people%20to%20understand%20how%20small%20choices%20that%20don't%20seem%20like%20major%20ethical%20choices%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20responsibility%20is%20to%20show%20up%20with%20high%20ethics%20in%20everything%20that%20you%20do%20and%20think%20about%20the%20bigger%20picture%20of%20how%20you%20do%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20firm%20had%20implemented%20programming%20through%20partnerships%20to%20help%20the%20company's%20leaders%20navigate%20the%20need%20to%20drive%20innovation%20ethically%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20place%20that%20we%20continue%20to%20invest%20because%20it's%20quite%20important%20for%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20is%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20is%20BCG%20on%20the%20adoption%20curve%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20and%20what%20do%20you%20want%20to%20see%20in%202025%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20excited%20about%20how%20BCG%20is%20driving%20change%20and%20grabbing%20the%20reins%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-companies-are-using-ai-generative-ai-daily-tasks-automation-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerative%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Gen%20AI%20is%20important%20to%20our%20clients%2C%20industry%2C%20and%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20suite%20of%20tools%2C%20some%20of%20which%20we%20developed%20internally%20and%20some%20that%20are%20available%20off%20the%20shelf%2C%20that%20we've%20made%20available%20to%20all%20of%20our%20staff.%20Nearly%20everyone%20is%20a%20user%20to%20some%20degree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20we're%20focused%20on%20now%20is%20moving%20from%20casual%20use%20to%20what%20we%20refer%20to%20as%20habitual%20use.%20It's%20habitual%20use%20that%20gets%20the%20value%20so%20that%20you%20can%20change%20how%20work%20gets%20done%2C%20based%20on%20the%20frequency%2C%20sophistication%2C%20and%20depth%20to%20which%20they%20use%20the%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20enablement%20resources%20for%20our%20people%2C%20both%20as%20individuals%20and%20as%20teams%2C%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20we're%20moving%20up%20that%20habitual%20usage%20curve%20as%20quickly%20as%20we%20can.%20A%20firm%20like%20BCG%20is%20under%20pressure%20to%20stay%20on%20top%20of%20things%20because%20its%20clients%20look%20to%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20do%20you%20strike%20that%20balance%20and%20not%20go%20so%20fast%20that%20you%20risk%20leaving%20some%20of%20your%20people%20behind%3F%20We%20have%20an%20enablement%20network%20of%20more%20than%20a%20thousand%20people%20who%20are%20there%20to%20help%20both%20individuals%20and%20teams%20adopt%20gen%20AI.%20It's%20in%20all%20of%20our%20core%20curriculums.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20this%20fall%2C%20we%20held%20AI%20days%20across%20every%20one%20of%20our%20offices%20at%20BCG%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fas-employee-confidence-in-ais-potential-grows-so-does-anxiety-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehands-on%20training%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%20we%20have%20people%20who%20are%20naturally%20there%20and%20ready%20for%20it%2C%20but%20we're%20also%20investing%20heavily%20to%20bring%20people%20up%20the%20curve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou've%20mentioned%20in%20Workforce%20Innovation-board%20roundtables%20that%20apprenticeship%20is%20now%20a%20two-way%20street.%20What%20advice%20would%20you%20give%20leaders%20looking%20to%20deploy%20apprenticeships%20differently%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20BCG%2C%20we're%20fortunate%20to%20have%20a%20pretty%20flat%20structure%20so%20that%20you%20always%20have%20a%20good%20proximity%20between%20your%20senior%20leaders%20and%20all%20your%20staff.%20There%20are%20two%20ways%20we%20focus%20on%20helping%20to%20support%20this%20idea%20of%20two-way%20mentorship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20is%20we%20just%20talk%20about%20topics.%20I%20recently%20wrote%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-publications.bcg.com%2F208-Weekly-Brief-Lets-Talk-About-Mental-Health.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epiece%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20a%20mental-health%20town%20hall%20we%20held.%20It%20was%20quite%20moving.%20We%20had%20BCG%20employees%20who%20were%20generous%20and%20vulnerable%20in%20talking%20to%20thousands%20of%20people%20on%20a%20virtual%20town-hall%20panel%20about%20their%20struggles%20with%20things%20like%20addiction%2C%20grief%2C%20and%20depression%2C%20both%20before%20their%20time%20at%20BCG%20and%20during%20their%20time%20at%20BCG%2C%20and%20how%20they%20work%20through%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20about%20having%20those%20difficult%20conversations%2C%20getting%20the%20points%20out%20there%2C%20and%20starting%20to%20have%20shared%20language%20or%20shared%20opportunities%20to%20talk%20about%20these%20topics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20days%20that%20I%20mentioned%20already%20are%20another%20way%20we%20do%20this.%20A%20lot%20of%20it%20is%20about%20getting%20cross-cohort%20connections%20on%20technology%20and%20other%20topics%2C%20creating%20forums%20so%20that%20people%20can%20talk%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20is%20ensuring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdouble-edged-sword-high-performers-face-at-work-feedback-managers-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtinual%2C%20structured%20feedback%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Our%20staff%20provides%20360-degree%20feedback%20all%20the%20time.%20It's%20an%20important%20part%20of%20what%20we%20do%2C%20and%20we're%20piloting%20doing%20it%20even%20more%20frequently.%20For%20example%2C%20we're%20giving%20people%20360%20feedback%20on%20how%20to%20be%20an%20inclusive%20leader.%20So%20it's%20both%20the%20formal%20mechanisms%20and%20also%20just%20creating%20the%20formats%20and%20discussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20much%20of%20culture%20and%20moving%20culture%20forward%20is%20really%20about%20having%20the%20language%20so%20we%20can%20share%20and%20talk%20about%20things.%20Creating%20those%20forums%20helps.%20It's%20an%20invitation%20to%20engage%20in%20productive%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20innovations%20are%20happening%20around%20DEI%2C%20especially%20as%20the%20topic%20has%20become%20more%20politicized%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-data-driven-strategies-tools-refine-dei-belonging-efforts-decisions-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDEI%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20built%20into%20our%20business%20model.%20We%20need%20great%20talent.%20We%20grow%20way%20faster%20than%20our%20talent%20pools%2C%20so%20just%20to%20get%20people%20in%20at%20quality%2C%20we%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20reach%20a%20lot%20of%20people%3B%20we%20need%20them%20to%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20business%20requires%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdei-evolves-as-the-culture-changes-and-ai-takes-hold-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einnovation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20requires%20diverse%20thought%20and%20experience.%20So%2C%20for%20us%2C%20it's%20quite%20core.%20One%20of%20my%20areas%20of%20focus%20is%20on%20inclusion%20and%20inclusive%20leadership.%20In%20some%20ways%2C%20it's%20the%20simplest%20thing%20to%20focus%20on.%20We%20all%20know%20that%20when%20people%20feel%20comfortable%20being%20themselves%20at%20work%2C%20you%20