.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JPC%20will%20hold%20discussions%20with%20representatives%20of%20all%20political%20parties.%20The%20other%20stakeholders%20will%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20process%20too%2C%20sources%20said.%20Speakers%20of%20all%20state%20assemblies%20can%20also%20be%20called%20along%20with%20intellectuals%20from%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20opinion%20of%20common%20people%20will%20also%20be%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20government%20wants%20to%20involve%20the%20people%20and%20the%20ways%20and%20means%20to%20achieve%20this%20can%20be%20discussed%20later%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChanging%20the%20current%20system%20will%20be%20extremely%20challenging%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20consensus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImplementing%20the%20%26quot%3BOne%20nation%20one%20election%26quot%3B%20plan%20would%20involve%20at%20least%20six%20bills%20to%20amend%20the%20Constitution%20and%20the%20government%20would%20require%20a%20two-thirds%20majority%20in%20parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20NDA%20has%20a%20simple%20majority%20in%20both%20houses%20of%20parliament%2C%20getting%20two-thirds%20majority%20in%20either%20house%20could%20be%20an%20uphill%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20245%20seats%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20NDA%20has%20112%2C%20the%20Opposition%20parties%2085.%20For%20a%20two-thirds%20majority%2C%20the%20government%20needs%20at%20least%20164%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20NDA%20has%20292%20of%20545%20seats.%20The%20two-thirds%20majority%20mark%20stands%20at%20364.%20%C2%A0But%20the%20situation%20could%20be%20dynamic%2C%20since%20the%20majority%20would%20be%20counted%20only%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20members%20present%20and%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20been%20pushing%20for%20simultaneous%20elections%20for%20a%20while%2C%20contending%20that%20the%20current%20system%20is%20a%20drain%20on%20time%2C%20money%20and%20effort.%20Then%20there%20is%20the%20question%20of%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%2C%20declared%20before%20elections%2C%20which%20puts%20brakes%20on%20development%20work%2C%20the%20government%20has%20pointed%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20called%20the%20idea%20impractical%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20logistical%20challenged%20the%20poll%20commission%20faces%20in%20just%20holding%20the%20state%20elections%20that%20sometimes%20run%20into%20multiple%20phases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20simultaneous%20election%20idea%20is%20also%20undemocratic%20and%20unconstitutional%2C%20the%20Opposition%20has%20contended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kovind%20report%20has%20suggested%20that%20the%20government%20create%20bipartisan%20support%20and%20a%20%C2%A0countrywide%20narrative.%20The%20implementation%20of%20%26quot%3BOne%20Nation%20One%20Election%26quot%3B%20can%20only%20happen%20after%202029%2C%20the%20report%20has%20recommended.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733759400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-04%2F0t4kpkig_election-generic-afp-_625x300_15_April_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fone-nation-one-election-bill-likely-in-this-session-of-parliament-may-be-sent-to-joint-parliamentary-committee-sources-7208435%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20is%20ready%20to%20launch%20its%20One%20Country%20One%20Election%20project%20and%20can%20introduce%20a%20bill%20in%20parliament%20in%20this%20session%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fone-nation-one-election-bill-likely-in-this-session-of-parliament-may-be-sent-to-joint-parliamentary-committee-sources-7208435%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Virat%20Kohli%20ki%20kamzori%20log%20pakad%20ke%20rakhe%20hue%20hai'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733759204000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22http