m%2Fphoto%2F116145551.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThurston%20County%20Commissioner%20Emily%20Clouse%20faces%20scrutiny%20following%20an%20investigation%20into%20her%20conduct.%20While%20cleared%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20retaliation%2C%20the%20investigation%20confirmed%20a%20romantic%20relationship%20with%20her%20former%20aide%2C%20Allyn%20Hershey%2C%20violating%20ethical%20guidelines.%20Clouse%20also%20borrowed%20money%20and%20accepted%20gifts%20from%20Hershey%2C%20further%20breaching%20ethical%20standards.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwho-is-emily-clouse-thurston-county-commissioner-facing-allegations-of-forcing-aide-into-relationship%2Farticleshow%2F116145551.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwho-is-emily-clouse-thurston-county-commissioner-facing-allegations-of-forcing-aide-into-relationship%2Famp_articleshow%2F116145551.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwho-is-emily-clouse-thurston-county-commissioner-facing-allegations-of-forcing-aide-into-relationship%2Famp_articleshow%2F116145551.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hoax%20Bomb%20Alert%2C%20Emergency%20Landing%20And%20Arrest%20Of%20'Intelligence%20Officer'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20bomb%20scare%20aboard%20a%20Nagpur-Kolkata%20flight%20that%20forced%20it%20to%20make%20an%20emergency%20landing%20in%20Chhattisgarh's%20capital%20city%20Raipur%20has%20sparked%20debate%20over%20the%20actions%20of%20both%20the%20informant%20and%20the%20authorities.%20While%20the%20flight's%20193%20occupants%20-%20187%20passengers%20and%20six%20crew%20members%20-%20were%20evacuated%20safely%2C%20the%20aftermath%20has%20left%20one%20flyer%2C%20who%20claims%20to%20be%20an%20intelligence%20officer%2C%20in%20legal%20limbo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2014%2C%20an%20emergency%20landing%20was%20made%20at%20Raipur%20Airport%20after%20a%20bomb%20threat%20alert.%20Security%20agencies%2C%20including%20the%20Central%20Industrial%20Security%20Force%20(CISF)%2C%20and%20bomb%20disposal%20units%2C%20conducted%20a%20meticulous%20search%20of%20the%20aircraft%20and%20passengers'%20luggage.%20No%20explosives%20were%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20preliminary%20information%2C%20the%20passenger%20told%20aircraft%20crew%20members%20about%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20bomb%20when%20the%20IndiGo%20flight%20was%20mid-air.%20The%20Air%20Traffic%20Control%20was%20informed%20and%20the%20flight%20was%20diverted%20to%20Raipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20behind%20the%20alert%2C%20Animesh%20Mandal%2C%20was%20arrested%20shortly%20after.%20His%20actions%20were%20deemed%20a%20hoax%2C%20and%20he%20was%20charged%20under%20Section%20351(4)%20of%20the%20BNS%20Act%20and%20Section%203(1)(g)%20of%20the%20Suppression%20of%20Unlawful%20Acts%20Against%20Civil%20Aviation%20Security%20Act%2C%201982.%20A%20local%20court%20sent%20him%20to%20judicial%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20in%20a%20surprising%20twist%2C%20Mr%20Mandal%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20an%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20(IB)%20officer%20and%20that%20he%20was%20acting%20in%20good%20faith%20by%20reporting%20the%20bomb%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20his%20lawyer%2C%20Faisal%20Rizvi%2C%20Mr%20Mandal%20received%20a%20message%20about%20a%20possible%20bomb%20on%20the%20flight%20and%20immediately%20alerted%20the%20crew.%20The%20crew%20informed%20the%20captain%2C%20prompting%20the%20emergency%20landing.%20When%20no%20bomb%20was%20found%2C%20the%20police%20arrested%20Mandal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnimesh%20Mandal%20was%20travelling%20to%20Kolkata%20after%20being%20transferred%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20Nagpur%20earlier%20this%20year.%20He%20shared%20the%20input%20as%20part%20of%20his%20duty%2C%20but%20instead%20of%20being%20recognized%20for%20his%20responsibility%2C%20he%20was%20arrested%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rizvi%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMandal%20remains%20in%20custody%20nearly%20a%20month%20later%2C%20entangled%20in%20procedural%20delays.%20The%201982%20Act%20mandates%20trial%20in%20a%20special%20court%2C%20which%20Chhattisgarh%20doesn't%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rizvi%20explained%2C%20%26quot%3BSection%203(1)(d)%20of%20the%20Act%20prescribes%20life%20imprisonment%20for%20such%20offences%2C%20but%20the%20case%20cannot%20proceed%20without%20a%20special%20court%20appointed%20by%20the%20High%20Court.%20This%20delay%20is%20prolonging%20Mandal's%20incarceration%2C%20and%20his%20critically%20ill%20parents%20add%20to%20his%20distress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20lawyer%20has%20alleged%20that%20despite%20reportedly%20presenting%20identity%20documents%20proving%20his%20affiliation%20with%20the%20IB%2C%20Mr%20Mandal's%20claims%20have%20been%20met%20with%20silence%20from%20the%20authorities.%20State%20Home%20Minister%20Vijay%20Sharma%2C%20in%20a%20brief%20remark%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20matter%20will%20have%20to%20be%20looked%20into.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733758560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fflight-generic-unsplash-650_625x300_1526441597302.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fa-hoax-bomb-alert-an-emergency-landing-and-arrest-of-intelligence-officer-7209885%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20recent%20bomb%20scare%20aboard%20a%20Nagpur-Kolkata%20flight%20that%20forced%20it%20to%20make%20an%20emergency%20landing%20in%20Chhattisgarh's%20capital%20city%20Raipur%20has%20sparked%20debate%20over%20the%20actions%20of%20both%20the%20informant%20and%20the%20authorities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fa-hoax-bomb-alert-an-emergency-landing-and-arrest-of-intelligence-officer-7209885%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22am