3B%20that%20allows%20terrorists%20and%20fundamentalists%20to%20act%20without%20restraint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20virtual%20address%20to%20a%20gathering%20of%20overseas%20Awami%20League%20supporters%20in%20London%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Ms%20Hasina%20accused%20Mr%20Yunus%20of%20being%20the%20%26quot%3Bmastermind%26quot%3B%20behind%20the%20July-August%20turmoil%20that%20ousted%20her%20government%20and%20vowed%20to%20bring%20him%20and%20his%20allies%20to%20justice%20under%20Bangladeshi%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20criticised%20Mr%20Yunus%20and%20his%20interim%20government%20for%20their%20alleged%20persecution%20of%20religious%20minorities%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20August%205%2C%20the%20attacks%20on%20minorities%2C%20places%20of%20worship%20of%20Hindus%2C%20Christians%20and%20Buddhists%20have%20been%20rampant.%20We%20condemn%20it.%20The%20Jamaat%20and%20terrorists%20are%20having%20a%20free%20run%20under%20the%20new%20regime%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20audio%20recording%20of%20Hasina's%20address%20was%20shared%20on%20the%20Facebook%20page%20of%20the%20Bangladesh%20Students'%20League%20and%20Bangladesh%20Awami%20League.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20remarks%20came%20as%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Vikram%20Misri%20is%20visiting%20to%20Dhaka%20today%20where%20he%20raised%20India's%20concerns%20over%20the%20safety%20of%20minorities%2C%20flagging%20%26quot%3Bregrettable%20incidents%20of%20attacks%20on%20cultural%2C%20religious%20and%20diplomatic%20properties%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20a%20spate%20of%20incidents%20of%20violence%20against%20Hindus%20and%20other%20minorities%2C%20as%20well%20as%20attacks%20on%20temples%20in%20Bangladesh%20in%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%20that%20triggered%20strong%20concerns%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBangladesh%20is%20now%20under%20the%20grip%20of%20a%20fascist%20regime%20where%20people's%20democratic%20rights%20have%20been%20obliterated.%20Our%20government's%20achievements%20in%20poverty%20alleviation%20and%20infrastructure%20development%2C%20strengthening%20of%20democracy%20were%20being%20undone%20under%20Yunus's%20leadership%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Hasina%20said%20during%20her%2037-minute%20virtual%20address%20over%20the%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Hasina%20accused%20the%20Yunus%20government%20of%20providing%20clemency%20to%20terrorists%20and%20criminals%2C%20including%20those%20involved%20in%20arson%20and%20murders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20release%20of%20convicted%20criminals%20and%20terrorists%2C%20including%20those%20responsible%20for%20attacks%20on%20the%20Bangladesh%20Parliament%20and%20other%20atrocities%2C%20proves%20the%20complicity%20of%20this%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Hasina%20vowed%20that%20those%20responsible%20for%20the%20alleged%20atrocities%20under%20the%20Yunus%20administration%20would%20be%20brought%20to%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMd%20Yunus%20and%20his%20allies%20are%20the%20masterminds%20of%20the%20July-August%20unrest%20in%20the%20country.%20They%20are%20behind%20the%20killing%20of%20students%20and%20policemen%2C%20arson%20and%20atrocities.%20The%20murderers%20and%20conspirators%20who%20have%20harmed%20our%20nation%20will%20be%20held%20accountable%20under%20Bangladeshi%20law.%20Just%20as%20we%20took%20action%20against%20war%20criminals%2C%20justice%20will%20prevail%20for%20today's%20wrongdoers.%20No%20one%20will%20escape%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%205%2C%20the%20student-led%20Monsoon%20Revolution%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20%26quot%3BStudents%20Against%20Discrimination%26quot%3B%20succeeded%20in%20toppling%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%2016-year%20regime%2C%20propelled%20by%20fervent%20demands%20for%20change%20and%20accountability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20unprecedented%20anti-government%20protests%2C%20Ms%20Hasina%20resigned%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20fled%20the%20country.%20She%20landed%20in%20India%20on%20August%205%20and%20is%20currently%20staying%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Hasina%20criticised%20Mr%20Yunus%20and%20his%20government%20for%20their%20alleged%20persecution%20of%20religious%20minorities%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20August%205%2C%20the%20attacks%20on%20minorities%2C%20places%20of%20worship%20of%20Hindus%2C%20Christians%20and%20Buddhists%20have%20been%20rampant.%20We%20condemn%20it.%20The%20Jamaat%20and%20terrorists%20are%20having%20a%20free%20run%20under%20the%20new%20regime%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Hasina%20expressed%20outrage%20over%20the%20judicial%20and%20administrative%20repression%20under%20the%20current%20government%2C%20citing%20the%20case%20of%20Hindu%20monk%20Chinmoy%20Krishna%20Das%20as%20an%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChinmoy%20Krishna%20Das'%20lawyer%20was%20barred%20from%20contesting%20his%20case%2C%20a%20blatant%20violation%20of%20legal%20rights.%20This%20government%20is%20using%20every%20tool%20to%20suppress%20dissent%20and%20deny%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinmay%20Krishna%20Das%2C%20a%20prominent%20spokesperson%20for%20Bangladesh%20Sammilita%20Sanatani%20Jagran%20Jote%2C%20was%20arrested%20at%20Dhaka's%20Hazrat%20Shahjalal%20International%20Airport%20on%20Monday%20while%20en%20route%20to%20Chattogram%20for%20a%20rally.%20He%20was%20denied%20bail%20and%20remanded%20to%20jail%20on%20Tuesday.%20His%20arrest%20has%20further%20fueled%20concerns%20over%20the%20treatment%20of%20Hindus%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECondemning%20the%20ongoing%20oppression%2C%20Hasina%20declared%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20dark%20chapter%20of%20our%20nation's%20history%20will%20not%20last%20forever.%20Mohammed%20Yunus%20will%20be%20held%20accountable%20for%20his%20actions%2C%20and%20justice%20will%20prevail.%26quot%3B%20Hasina%20further%20alleged%20that%20people%20are%20being%20subjected%20to%20brutal%