Syria%20is%20a%20series%20of%20events%20that%20are%20unfolding%20because%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20miscalculation%26quot%3B%20by%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20Iran's%20tentacles%20in%20the%20region%20have%20been%20cut%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Azar%20said%2C%20explaining%20that%20%26quot%3BIran%20and%20Hezbollah%20made%20a%20huge%20miscalculation.%20They%20didn't%20understand%20what%20the%20consequences%20would%20be%20of%20the%20attack%20against%20Israel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20added%20that%20%26quot%3BHezbollah%20has%20been%20hit%20very%20hard.%20Nasrallah%2C%20as%20you%20remember%2C%20was%20taken%20out%2C%20along%20with%20many%20thousands%20of%20Hezbollah%20terrorists.%20Then%20Iran%20attacked%20Israel%20directly%2C%20and%20as%20you%20know%2C%20Israel%20defended%20itself%20and%20retaliated%20hard.%20So%20when%20you%20look%20at%20the%20picture%20today%2C%20you%20see%20that%20these%20tentacles%20of%20the%20Iranian%20regime%20have%20all%20been%20cut.%20And%20now%2C%20rebel%20forces%20in%20the%20region%20(Syria)%2C%20which%20have%20been%20following%20all%20that%20(happened)%20and%20seeing%20the%20debilitation%20of%20the%20Iran%20axis%20took%20full%20advantage%20of%20it.%20And%20that%20is%20how%20you%20see%20the%20change%20in%20Syria.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Azar%20said%20that%20the%20situation%20in%20Syria%20is%20a%20consequence%20of%20Iran%20messing%20with%20Israel%2C%20however%2C%20it%20is%20not%20engineered%20by%20Tel%20Aviv.%20%26quot%3BIsrael%20is%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20Syrian%20conflict.%20We%20are%20not%20intending%20to%20involve%20ourselves%20in%20Syrian%20politics.%20That%20is%20a%20matter%20that%20the%20Syrian%20people%20have%20to%20sort%20out%20for%20themselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESITUATION%20AT%20THE%20ISRAEL-SYRIA%20BORDER%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Azar%20said%20that%20Tel%20Aviv%20is%20always%20prepared%20to%20defend%20itself%20against%20any%20and%20all%20threats%2C%20and%20that%20is%20what%20they%20are%20limiting%20themselves%20to%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsrael%20is%20no%20doubt%20in%20a%20situation%20of%20alert.%20We%20are%20following%20very%20closely%20the%20events%20in%20Syria.%20The%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%20have%20already%20taken%20defensive%20positions%20in%20the%20buffer%20zone%20in%20the%20border%20between%20Israel%20and%20Syria%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Azar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20disengagement%20zone%20that%20was%20created%20in%201974%20following%20the%20Yom%20Kippur%20War.%20That%20zone%20is%20a%20buffer%20zone%20from%20several%20hundred%20metres%20to%20a%20few%20kilometres.%20It%20is%20located%20in%20the%20north.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20that%20area%20has%20been%20attacked%20by%20different%20groups.%20It%20has%20been%20attacked%20now%20too.%20The%20UN%20forces%20there%20have%20come%20under%20attack%20and%20Israel%20has%20come%20to%20the%20rescue.%20So%20we%20are%20taking%20this%20temporary%20defensive%20positions%20in%20the%20buffer%20zone%20and%20following%20very%20closely%20what%20is%20going%20on%20on%20the%20other%20side%2C%20preparing%20to%20defend%20ourselves%20against%20any%20possible%20attack%20or%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESITUATION%20IN%20A%20GIST%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBashar%20Al-Assad's%20regime%20was%20backed%20by%20Russia%2C%20Iran%2C%20and%20Tehran-backed%20Hezbollah%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsyria-civil-war-all-about-the-rebels-behind-the-fall-of-bashar-al-assad-7205678%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20rebels%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20led%20by%20Abu%20Mohammad%20Al-Jolani%2C%20a%20terrorist%20formerly%20associated%20with%20Al%20Qaeda%20and%20ISIS.%20While%20Turkey%20backs%20some%20of%20the%20rebel%20groups%20against%20the%20Al-Assads%2C%20Al-Jolani%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Hayat%20Tahrir%20Al-Sham%20or%20HTS%20-%20the