w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241026-WA0034-1_11zon-1733381439-1200x900.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241026-WA0034-1_11zon-1733381439-800x600.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241026-WA0034-1_11zon-1733381439-600x450.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241026-WA0034-1_11zon-1733381439-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241026-WA0034-1_11zon-1733381439-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241026-WA0034-1_11zon-1733381439-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-386493%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAfter%20years%20of%20persistence%2C%20the%20couple%20proudly%20opened%20their%20first%20official%20Sreshte%20store%20in%20Guntur%20in%202019%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20demand%20for%20organic%20products%20continues%20to%20grow%2C%20Sreshte%20has%20expanded%20its%20product%20range%20to%20include%20over%20160%20items.%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20we%20offer%20everything%20from%20organic%20rice%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328846%2Fsibi-manivannan-runs-gramiya-cold-pressed-oils-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecold-pressed%20oils%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20homemade%20powders%20like%20peanut%20and%20sprouted%20ragi%20powder%2C%20along%20with%20Himalayan%20pink%20salt%2C%20black%20salt%2C%20and%20a%20variety%20of%20flakes%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manikanta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20essentials%2C%20Sreshte%20has%20ventured%20into%20ready-to-eat%20items.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20recently%20started%20offering%20homemade%20sweets%2C%20snacks%2C%20and%20cupcakes%20made%20from%20millets%2C%20jaggery%2C%20and%20palm%20jaggery%20%E2%80%94%20healthy%20alternatives%20to%20rice%20flour%2C%20refined%20flour%2C%20and%20white%20sugar%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Manikanta.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20customers%20are%20keen%20on%20organic%20products%2C%20but%20they%20often%20struggle%20to%20trust%20their%20authenticity.%20To%20address%20this%2C%20we%20invite%20them%20to%20visit%20the%20farms%2C%20and%20if%20they%20wish%2C%20they%20can%20directly%20order%20from%20the%20farmers%2C%20with%20us%20handling%20the%20delivery%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESreshte%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20authenticity%20is%20reflected%20in%20their%20traditional%20processing%20methods.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20vacuum%20packing%20and%20oxygen%20absorbers%20to%20prevent%20pests%20naturally%2C%20without%20relying%20on%20preservatives%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manikanta.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20process%20that%20helps%20us%20maintain%20the%20freshness%20and%20quality%20of%20our%20products.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20five%20years%20of%20operation%2C%20Sreshte%20has%20reached%20impressive%20milestones%2C%20generating%20a%20monthly%20income%20of%20Rs%207.5%20lakh%20and%20an%20annual%20turnover%20of%20Rs%2090%20lakh.%20However%2C%20for%20Manikanta%20and%20Pavani%2C%20the%20true%20measure%20of%20success%20goes%20beyond%20financial%20achievements.%20They%20take%20immense%20pride%20in%20the%20positive%20impact%20they%20have%20on%20their%20customers%E2%80%99%20health%20and%20well-being.%20%E2%80%9COur%20aim%20is%20to%20encourage%20people%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20what%20they%20eat%20and%20embrace%20healthier%20choices%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manikanta.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20organic%20food%20to%20become%20a%20way%20of%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20farmers%20and%20the%20local%20communi